HEADWORD: Polytocous
<hw>Po*lyt"o*cous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/;
<grk>poly`s</grk> many + <?/ offspring.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Bearing fruit repeatedly, as most perennial
plants; polycarpic.</def>⟦br⟧
